name: Mrs. Ndruwo
description:
Ndruwo/ Gendruwo is a Javanese myth about a spirits that  has a visual look like a human-like their body is covered with thick hair. Genderuwo is known most widely in the community on the island of Java, Indonesia. Their favorite place are watery rocks, old buildings, large shady trees or damp, quiet and dark corners. Such an introvert aren't they?

Ndruwo common gender is known as a male, this time I represent a female Ndruwo, who love the corner and quite.
